To install,

1.  Copy to the system xkb dir: sudo cp cyborg16 /usr/share/X11/xkb/symbols/
2.  Test: setxkbmap cyborg16 basic # replace basic with desired variant, e.g. colemak_ch
3.  Set permanently.
    
    Debian: edit /etc/default/keymap (or something like that)
    
    Fedora: edit /etc/X11/xorg.conf.d/00-keyboard.conf

